<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Home</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #faf8f5 0%, #f0ebe3 100%);
      color: #2c2a26;
      min-height: 100vh;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    nav {
      padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(44, 42, 38, 0.08);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #2c2a26;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: color 0.25s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #c45c41;
    }

    nav a.active {
      color: #c45c41;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #1a1917;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #5a564f;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #4a4742;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .accent {
      color: #c45c41;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="active">Home</a>
    <a href="/about">About</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
  <main>
    <h1>Welcome Home</h1>
    <p class="tagline">A place to rest and dream</p>
    <p>This is a simple, elegant space built with care. No clutter, no noiseâ€”just clarity and warmth.</p>
    <p>Feel free to explore <a href="/about" class="accent">who we are</a> or <a href="/contact" class="accent">get in
        touch</a>.</p>
  </main>
</body>

</html>